{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Jhon-Crow/One-try/pulls/22","id":3584565905,"node_id":"PR_kwDOSHj2o87VqCKR","html_url":"https://github.com/Jhon-Crow/One-try/pull/22","diff_url":"https://github.com/Jhon-Crow/One-try/pull/22.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/Jhon-Crow/One-try/pull/22.patch","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Jhon-Crow/One-try/issues/22","number":22,"state":"open","locked":false,"title":"feat(engine): migrate project from Unity to Godot 4","user":{"login":"konard","id":1431904,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1431904?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard","html_url":"https://github.com/konard","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"body":"## Summary\n\nCloses #21 — migrates the entire project from Unity 6.3 LTS to **Godot 4.3** (free, open-source, no account or license required).\n\n### What changed\n\n- **Removed** all Unity-specific files: `Assets/`, `Packages/`, `ProjectSettings/`\n- **Added** Godot 4.3 project:\n  - `project.godot` — engine config (Godot 4.3, Forward+ renderer, 1920×1080)\n  - `export_presets.cfg` — Windows Desktop export preset\n  - `icon.svg` — project icon\n  - `scenes/main.tscn` — main scene equivalent to the Unity SampleScene (camera, directional light, level with plane + falling sphere, win-screen UI \"A WINNER IS YOU\")\n  - `scenes/player_mannequin.tscn` — multi-part humanoid mannequin built from BoxMesh primitives, matching the Unity capsule hierarchy; idle breathing animation via AnimationPlayer\n  - `scripts/player_character.gd` — GDScript port of `PlayerCharacter.cs` (idle animation trigger, `face_direction()` hook for future locomotion)\n  - `scripts/game_controller.gd` — shows win screen on signal\n  - `scripts/win_trigger.gd` — Area3D trigger that fires when the sphere lands\n- **Replaced** `.github/workflows/build.yml` — Unity/GameCI workflow → Godot headless export workflow. **No secrets or credentials required** — Godot downloads automatically from official GitHub releases.\n- **Updated** `.gitignore`, `README.md`, `GAME_DESIGN.md` to reflect Godot.\n\n### CI/CD\n\nThe new workflow:\n1. Downloads Godot 4.3 headless binary from the official GitHub release\n2. Downloads Godot export templates\n3. Imports the project (generates the `.godot/` cache)\n4. Exports a Windows EXE via `godot --headless --export-release \"Windows Desktop\"`\n5. Zips and uploads as a workflow artifact `OneTry-Win64-<run-number>`\n\nNo Unity account, no `UNITY_EMAIL`/`UNITY_PASSWORD` secrets needed.\n\n## How to reproduce / verify\n\n1. Open the project in Godot 4.3 (File → Import → select repo folder).\n2. Press **F5** — a sphere falls onto a plane; \"A WINNER IS YOU\" appears on collision.\n3. Drag `scenes/player_mannequin.tscn` into the scene — mannequin plays idle breathing loop.\n4. Check GitHub Actions: the `Build Portable Windows EXE` workflow completes without any secrets configured.","created_at":"2026-04-25T23:26:49Z","updated_at":"2026-04-26T07:21:30Z","closed_at":null,"merged_at":null,"merge_commit_sha":"125ae9991fdf96084ad3daa4037fb8ded91a7cbd","assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[],"requested_teams":[],"labels":[],"milestone":null,"draft":false,"commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Jhon-Crow/One-try/pulls/22/commits","review_comments_url":"https://api.github.com